'''''Star Wars: The Official Magazine'' 27''', also styled as '''''Star Wars'' Magazine 27''',  was the 27th issue of the ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]''. It largely reprinted content from [[Star Wars Insider 49|''Star Wars Insider'' 49]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*[[Feel the Force]]
*[[Prequel Update]]
*[[Jawa's Corner]]
*[[In the Star Wars Universe|In the ''Star Wars'' Universe]] &mdash; [[John Ratzenberger]] {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 49}}
*[[Bookshelf|''Star Wars'' Bookshelf]] &mdash; When the Empire Struck Books {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 49}}
*[[The Horse's Mouth]] &mdash; Episode V Depicted in Comics: The Shadowy Edge of Empire {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 49}}
*[[Comlink (department)|Comlink]]

===Features===
*"[[Prequel Update]]"
*"[[Director Irvin Kershner]]" {{C|from [[Star Wars Insider 49|''Star Wars Insider'' 49]]}}
*"[[Lawrence Kasdan: Screenwriter]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 49}}
*"[[James Earl Jones: Voice of Vader]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 49}}
*"[[Lando Calrissian: Billy Dee Williams]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 49}}
*"[[The Ultimate Empire Strikes Back Insider's Guide|The Ultimate ''Empire Strikes Back'' Insider's Guide]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 49}}

